    "title": "第1話",
    "enTitle": "",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "大雨が降ったある日のこと。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 61,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": 6224754148953661164,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "その日のトレーニングは室内で筋トレをする予定だったので、\r\n自分たちには影響がないと思っていたのだが――",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 112,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": -2284416496152402663,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "嗚呼、水が滴るボクも美しい……。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 127,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "なんで濡れてるんだ！？",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 4
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "なんで濡れてるの！？",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 4
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 39,
                    "pathId": -6711562590110851081
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 7168747795471937215
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 125,
                    "pathId": -5797667339456364315
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": -4523728602572441547
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1587125465421011490,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "空がボクの姿を見たいと泣き出したんだ。\r\n外に出て天を慰めるのも、王の務めさ。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 263,
            "voiceIdx": 1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 199,
                    "pathId": 7472196920015637139
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 81,
                    "pathId": -394995128033686905
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 24,
                    "pathId": -1708847348556463435
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 18,
                    "pathId": -1976991747622792556
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4819570426919914456,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そして一歩外に出れば始まる、ボクと雨のアンサンブル。\r\n――本当に最高だった。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 259,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 167,
                    "pathId": 7272548610217352114
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": -2215723159139998520
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2088980934993713864,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "荒れる風と共にコースを走り、光る雨粒で飾られた\r\nボクの姿はまさに……パーフェクト！！",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 272,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "この大雨の中、走ったのか！？",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 7
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "この大雨の中、走ったの！？",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 7
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": -7392060974643835562
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": 383866169980231486
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6537816689859243565,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "勿論だとも！",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 56,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -5136173228461612466
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": 4522557837707889282
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8471817132524189775,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "大雨の中であれ重バ場であれ、ボクの走りは力強く、美しい。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 208,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": 5180600828115929498
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": 1649804694102118073
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8927160673288428691,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "その走りを望む者がいる限り……、\r\nどのような舞台であろうとも、ボクはステージに立ち続けるのさ。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 258,
            "voiceIdx": 6,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "どんな悪天候でも？",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 10
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -565891435864463108
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 7213381440703741194
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8102392159429963851,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "はーっはっはっはっは！　当然だよ。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 122,
            "voiceIdx": 7,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -7631114184707197550
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 804710296182965183
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6437932845342518266,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ボクが目指しているのは“世紀末覇王”。\r\nこの世界を照らす絶対的で唯一無二の存在だ。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 286,
            "voiceIdx": 8,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 231,
                    "pathId": -3760059239335122619
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": 1086311317432048536
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8201158684600430735,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "たとえ雨が降ろうが雪が降ろうが、障害にすらならないよ。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 178,
            "voiceIdx": 9,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 68,
                    "pathId": 659222159784625338
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 45,
                    "pathId": 8674401876380344536
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2672801277926658127,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "むしろ、天候程度でやる気を失うようじゃ、\r\n“世紀末覇王”には到底なれないさ。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 229,
            "voiceIdx": 10,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 8019593977732306242
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -5980631232418980218
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2790845565813562292,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……おやおや、トレーナー君。\r\nそんなまじまじと見つめて……ボクに見惚れてしまったのかい？",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 240,
            "voiceIdx": 11,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "熱い志だな",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 15
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "熱い志だね",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 15
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -6159527696274246608
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -4223211764297796236
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 419450118560784253,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ふっ、何を今さら。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "voiceIdx": 12,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 63,
                    "pathId": -4803695152797185178
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": -2742337385688365656
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6366006168560490858,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "しかしいい着眼点だ。もっとじっくりボクへの感想を聞かせたまえ。\r\n心の底からボクを褒めたたえるといい！",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 368,
            "voiceIdx": 13,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": -7724194513475814333
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 8566441130623101998
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3583409260083600358,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "全ての褒め言葉はボクのために存在する！！\r\nさあ、さあ！　トレーナーく……くしゅん！",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 269,
            "voiceIdx": 14,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 8928357899022716914
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 16,
                    "pathId": 7709903356460782152
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4102082533358917580,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "テイエムオペラオーの足元には大きな水たまりができ始めている。\r\nこのままだと風邪をひいてしまうことだろう。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 114,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "着替えてきたら……？",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 19
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": 6408806692816453274
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": 6099133706026466237
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1074378314937584310,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ん？　別にボクはこのままでも……。\r\nはっ！　もしかしてトレーナー君、君は……。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 240,
            "voiceIdx": 15,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": 2750881642530755703
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 42,
                    "pathId": -7325300054486153914
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2146936774167195490,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "濡れて一段とつややかになったボクの姿に、\r\n照れてしまったというのかい？",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 178,
            "voiceIdx": 16,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 98,
                    "pathId": -6673360316689079801
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 3982280171780175658
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3386312582399642300,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "わかる、わかるよその気持ち！　ボクという\r\n絶対的な美を前にして、羞恥心が芽生えてしまったんだろう？",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 256,
            "voiceIdx": 17,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "いいから着替えてくるんだ！",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 22
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "いいから着替えてきなさい！",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 22
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -3487623644095364950
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 41,
                    "pathId": 5534167432388927039
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3237949976434074484,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "と、トレーナー君！？",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 57,
            "voiceIdx": 18,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": 1045026836750228293
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": -8424352285581324874
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5961073209046432746,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "いつまでも部屋から出ようとしないテイエムオペラオーを、\r\nなんとかして部屋の外に追い出した。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": 8642134259365307482
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": 2325062565080370294
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6078556655769513552,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "全く、勝手に部屋から追い立てて……。\r\n本当に君はよかったのかい？",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 192,
            "voiceIdx": 19,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 54,
                    "pathId": 7306723092031129362
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 55,
                    "pathId": -1934125480476475903
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 37856185982552030,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "水に濡れたボクを堪能する、\r\nせっかくの機会を逃すなんて……。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 155,
            "voiceIdx": 20,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "風邪をひいたら困るから",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 26
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": 6342469331420178704
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 114,
                    "pathId": -6235334820475494248
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7353499228799232908,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "おやおや、そんな訪れない未来など心配しなくてもいいよ。\r\n君が信じる未来はひとつだけでいい。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 273,
            "voiceIdx": 21,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 227,
                    "pathId": 3290214695506460074
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": -5642702372606962200
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2418021224371532484,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ボクが“世紀末覇王”となり、\r\n世界を照らすということだけをさ。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 169,
            "voiceIdx": 22,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": 3110667334287737356
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -2021913885355640642
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5035678843168984171,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "では、今日のトレーニングに励むとしようか。\r\nまさかこのボクが、日課をサボるわけにはいかないからね。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 265,
            "voiceIdx": 23,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "でもジャージはまだ濡れているんじゃ……",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 29
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": 8572744431199381127
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -165396317857677976
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4160416905036902991,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ああ、だから制服で走ろう！\r\n場所は河川敷がいいかな、まさに青春チックにね！",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 284,
            "voiceIdx": 24,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 200,
                    "pathId": 1770835194506810091
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 32,
                    "pathId": 971393915316822289
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7240068854724671293,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テイエムオペラオー",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "はためくスカート、力強いボクの走りと雨のコントラスト。\r\n嗚呼……最高のシチュエーションになりそうだ！！",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 315,
            "voiceIdx": 25,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 64,
                    "pathId": -4830919256080133953
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": 3595371982637652169
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -455649867359329393,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そう言って制服のまま外に駆けだそうとする\r\nテイエムオペラオーを、必死に止めることになったのだった。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 110,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
